	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Apart from A) the PowerPak's predictable initialization and B) any errors in the mapper logic, the PowerPak will preform EXACTLY the same as a "repro". If the games don't work reliably on the PowerPak, they probably don't work reliably in a "repro", especially since without a doubt the PowerPak's UNROM and MMC1 mappers are OK.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


